aces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf830f86d1ee8a926a14a6c657d2f4eff4fadd8","tid":462202,"uid":101303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"小弟我都同你一樣，返學放學搵女朋友<br />\n雖然係u係有朋友，但大家放學都忙(eg搞莊，拍拖，grp pj)，所以放學好多時都係自己走<br />\n明明係想比多d安全感佢先唔上莊唔識異性，但反而搞到自己有d毒...<br />\n有時係到諗如果有日無左佢咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d516fe72c63e5d488659f3621edca182e8c5bae","tid":462202,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"唉同我一撚樣啊<br />\n成日都想擺好多心機落女朋友到<br />\n又怕佢擔心 唔會搵女仔做朋友 最多傾下project 就算<br />\n但係又見佢愛自己&gt;&gt;&gt;溫書&gt;&gt;與趣&gt;朋友&gt;我<br />\n會諗自己擺咁多時間比佢係咪唔值<br />\n但係又做唔出唔理佢嘅行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪毒撚拍拖先會咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7e6431a9e1ef02bc26862633beadf1fea47523","tid":462202,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"個個都愛自己多d既話點磨合？<br />\n總有一方係付出多d架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：一樣處境，有不滿同對方講就會比人屌返轉頭，一星期嘈幾次交，就黎挨唔住"},{"pid":"b747c37a850c24f440da9287ad0ad386d71d859c","tid":462202,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"世界得番ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b74e4a1ac1804c060f37f6d3801a0fa7652a07","tid":462202,"uid":71703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界得番ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要學識放低呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知實有難度，但我好愛我女友，以前d野唔記得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a5f31c4b0420a21c590e2f0f5bd1e11cd914b7","tid":462202,"