方離開你您嘅時候您就真係變到咩都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82ad2aadca997994176ef70af49b5f6e2c17ad6","tid":462202,"uid":143936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T19:20:37.000Z","msg":"巴打 同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好愛我男朋友<br />\n自己冇乜fd 所有時間都係投放哂係佢身上<br />\n佢一唔揾我 我就好唔放心<br />\n覺得佢同其他人傾計多過我好多 <br />\n我好似變得唔重要<br />\n加上我控制欲好強<br />\n之前因爲哩個問題我嘗試講分手 <br />\n無謂辛苦大家<br />\n但佢冇放棄我 一直挽留<br />\n宜家少左在意佢online唔係同我講野<br />\n不過都會有時sad<br />\n因為我地唔同u已經少接觸 <br />\n再加上佢覺得都拍左幾年拖<br />\n佢覺得感情昇華到老夫老妻模式<br />\n唔洗講出口掛住我 佢個心一直都有<br />\n但我太過中意佢 乜都好在意 <br />\n我宜家為有減少care佢既心態 盡量比自己抽離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec37f28df61159504189d72224f98da944184b1","tid":462202,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T21:52:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線好chur啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ea5e6476dbc1dd684e8a6932622427a1c4ab1d","tid":462202,"uid":70022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T21:56:48.000Z","msg":"對佢太好 唔會珍惜架 冇左吸引力<br />\n搵返自己世界啦 人係犯賤架  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1f3fa3702bdd191b696b98ac35ea9242f85f1d","tid":462202,"uid":13910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對佢太好 唔會珍惜架 冇左吸引力<br />\n搵返自己世界啦 人係犯賤架  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以點樣搵返自己個世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bb63b80fe0e28c7fc9d62f134d968cbbba0d4e","tid